<s> yup, a busy screen is a disaster, I am not sure about the solution.  </s>
<s> People with AADD that I worked with benefited from color highlighting and the use of color for emphasis of structure.  </s>
<s> I adopted a template at work for specks and minutes specifically with AADD in mind were color was a major part of helping people focus on that they needed to know.  </s>
<s> The change in productivity was astounding.  </s>
<s> People new what they needed to know.  </s>
<s> I would not recommend to people to publish a 10,000 word specification document (I kid you not) without use of color and expect persons with ADD to find the information that they need.  </s>
